Personal lifeWood married magician Geoffrey Durham in March 1980. They separated in October 2002.   They have two children, Grace (born 1988) and Henry (born 1992). Although Wood fiercely maintains her privacy and that of her children, even originally refusing to publicly release the name of her son when he was born, Henry Durham appeared in a small cameo in her 2010 BBC Christmas Special.Wood is a Quaker  and a vegetarian, once remarking; "I'm all for killing animals and turning them into handbags. I just don't want to have to eat them." Wood lives in Highgate, North London.
