Eleonore      She married Hugh David Campbell in 1954 and has seven daughters. She lives with her family in Waitsfield, Vermont.   
Johannes       Married 1969 to Lynne Peterson and has one son, Sam von Trapp, and one daughter, Kristina von Trapp-Frame. Johannes manages the family resort in Stowe, Vermont, with his son Sam.     

